Sub-policy 0
https://wasabi-apps.co.jp/privacypolicy/policyen.html:
Wasabi Applications K.K. (hereinafter referred to as "our company") provides smartphone applications (including tablet applications). This privacy policy explains how we use the personal data we collect from you when you use our smartphone applications.
Please note that the data collected through our website, its inquiry form, or contact to our support are treated separately from this privacy policy because the data handled is different. Please refer to the
"Website and Inquiry Privacy Policy."
Also, when the consent form for the use of personal data is displayed in the app, please refer to
this for the minimal necessary consent items to display basic, non-personalized ads
. (
