Sub-policy 1
https://wasabi-apps.co.jp/privacypolicy/policyweben.html:
Wasabi Applications K.K. (hereinafter referred to as "our company") provides various information related to our company on the website and accepts your questions and opinions through the inquiry form. We also provide a support email address. This privacy policy explains how our company uses the personal data we collect from you when you use our website and make inquiries.
Please note that data collected through the use of our smartphone app is handled separately because it is different from this privacy policy. Please refer to the
"Privacy Policy for Smartphone Applications."
